What is OTT Advertising Services?
OTT Advertising Services represent the integration of real‑time data, machine learning, and cloud‑based infrastructure to deliver video advertising directly to consumers on the internet, free from the constraints of linear broadcasting. Unlike traditional TV advertising, OTT ads can be dynamically inserted, tracked, and optimized across numerous platforms, devices, and geographies, providing an unprecedented level of personalization and reach to brands, agencies, and content creators.

In an era where consumers increasingly prefer on‑demand streaming, OTT advertising services have become a pivotal component of modern media strategies. By leveraging the power of programmatic acquisition, audience segmentation, and advanced measurement, advertisers can achieve high engagement, measurable performance, and scalable return on investment.

